686
00:43:32,960 --> 00:43:34,235
Meu pai.

687
00:43:36,720 --> 00:43:38,234
Dr. Murry.

688
00:43:41,000 --> 00:43:42,229
Companheiro bonito.

689
00:43:47,280 --> 00:43:49,192
